snippet.title: Extra Song Pack vol.1 Trailer [Touhou Danmaku Kagura Phantasia Lost]
snippet.description:
"Touhou Danmaku Kagura Phantasia Lost" will finally be released on Steam, on February 8, 2024!
The first DLC,  released alongside the Steam version, contains 25 songs, including 1 Touhou original song.

https://store.steampowered.com/app/2190220
Released along the Steam version

_____
Presented by Unknown X

○Touhou Danmaku Kagura Phantasia Lost - Official website
https://danmaku.jp/phantasia-lost/en/
